cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SD

This paper discusses latent variable modeling in the context of deep generative models, specifically variational autoencoders and generative adversarial networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also touches on the geometry of latent spaces, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.SD (Software Engineering).
